`landing_cloner` lets you take a landing page (from a constructor or any public URL), clone it into a **self-hosted Flask project**, and fully control it â€” no platform limits, no traffic restrictions, no vendor lock-in.

Perfect for marketers, indie hackers, and developers who want **ownership** over their landing pages.

